* For customizations, change the following files:

config.inc.php
subnets.inc.php

* Make sure you allow mysql access among all the servers. For example:

From mysql on Uris, do:
mysql> GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES on dhcp.* to dhcp@128.59.219.2 identified by '<password>';

From mysql on Culbs, do:
mysql> GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES on dhcp.* to dhcp@128.59.205.3 identified by '<password>';

* Make sure you have the dhcp/queue directory with following criteria:
drwx------    2 apache   root         4096 Dec 17 16:40 queue/

